Deploy Endgame
Can deploy inband through the GUI or out of band with a script
ENDGAME: Deploy a Sensor to Win(In-Band Mgmt): Endgame Admin Guide(Page 90-93)
1. Endpoints / Action Toolbar: Discover Endpoints
1.1: enter ip range / custom port / start scan / finish
2. After “Scan Completed” /action toolbar: Windows Tab
3. Select endpoints
4. Actions: Deploy
5. Deploy Sensor
5.1: Select Sensor / Domain Name / Username / Password
6. Deploy Sensors / Close
7. Action Toolbar: select Windows tab / Active tab
8. Verify Endpoints (with sensor installed) in list as hostname of endpoint

ENDGAME: Create Custom Rule: Endgame Admin Guide (Page 68-75) bottom of page
1. Administration / Rules tab / Create Rule Wizard
1.1: Compose EQL Query
1.2: Classify Alert
1.3: Name Rule
2. Enable Custom Rule: In Endpoint Policy list select policy to enable
3. On Enpoint Policy config page, select Adversary Behaviors
4. Select appropriate rule (toggle on)
